					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That's funny. I was pondering the idea of converting Metroid to MMC3 just yesterday. It would make it easier to expand ROMs by providing a larger capacity and doing away with the awkward serial interface that causes problems if you want to bank swap on both the NMI and main thread.</div>

